{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we each had a suitcase with us and all our personal stuff like watches, rings, the bit of jewelry that remained that wasn't sold.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a watch, a gold watch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had a ring that I got, 12th birthday, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had a chain which my grandmother gave me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I didn't want to part with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I was wearing it all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we loaded onto these cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were locked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And on the trip to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, Majdanek was just outside Lublin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And luckily, it wasn't all that far away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I can't remember how long that journey took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a nightmare because it was our first experience of being herded into these cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was no food given on the journey, as far as I remember, no water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we arrived in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they got us out of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You had to jump.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "These trucks were very high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was no ladders, no steps to help us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had to just get off it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And literally herded to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then we were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The men were separated from the women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were taken to a bath house or whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Cold water, the middle of winter, and you're just stripped, leave all your belongings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And you were given, when you came out it shivering.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that was the first time I saw the SS women that were-- they were Nazi guards, the women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were very, very cruel, all of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the one that was in charge of them was particularly-- I remember her as if it was yesterday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Her name was Elsa Erich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She had eyes like glass, steel.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
